            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fries are cooking, peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your<strong> chicken breast strips</strong> into bite-sized pieces, then add to a bowl with your <strong>garam masala</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spiced chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1629801244893-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
