            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>spiced chicken </strong>to the<strong> beaten egg </strong>and give it a good mix up, then add it to the <strong>breadcrumbs </strong>and toss until nicely coated all over</p><p>Transfer the<strong> breaded chicken pieces</strong> to a separate baking tray (or two!) and put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until golden and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>Keralan-style popcorn chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
