    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, peel and grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>grated carrot </strong>to<strong> </strong>a bowl with the juice of your <strong>lime[s]</strong>, <strong>nigella seeds</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>zesty carrot slaw</strong></p>",
